{"tid":1397840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[太古人被維穩?] 出罷工post就比人禁言兼且踢出Group","createTime":"2019-08-02T15:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:49:09.000Z","uid":172435,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"59536b8d176e96820739bdc8bdb33ae87e3c78e6","tid":1397840,"uid":172435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"事源係喺FB 太古人太古事 嘅Group入邊<br />\n<br />\n有第一個人post咗呢兩張相，之後比Admin審查唔批。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/txB6Z7S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtxB6Z7S.png&h=185fc8fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5O6VTsS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5O6VTsS.png&h=54cc7b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後有第二個人再post, 唔洗半個鐘比Admin禁言唔得出聲。<br />\n<br />\n再有第三個人post, 今次Admin有出現喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDGCntg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDGCntg.png&h=c102a24f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OqUkkeX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqUkkeX.png&h=3671b5bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQCYRmE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQCYRmE.png&h=d85346c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tXmO8j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tXmO8j.png&h=7ef37a4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/px160e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpx160e0.png&h=96224ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾呢個post係del咗，仲踢走出post嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n三個人都係post同一樣嘅嘢，<br />\n究竟Admin有幾鍾意返工？<br />\n<br />\n呢位Admin 同時兼任幾個區Groups 嘅Admin, <br />\n包括：<br />\n太古人太古事<br />\n油塘人油塘事<br />\n筲箕灣人筲箕灣事<br />\n啟德人啟德事<br />\n柴灣人柴灣事 <br />\n<br />\n仲話係&rdquo;訪問&rdquo;人地區Group, <br />\n有錢到咁住哂咁多區？叻！<br />\n<br />\n一齊黎睇下五區Admin英姿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjsBCYM.png\